body:
**  This mod makes the Create mod compatible with other mods that contain metals. Now, ores and metals can be crushed into their crushed versions, with which you can do everything that you can do with regular crushed ores from Create. Also, these crushed ores can be smelted in furnaces from TConstruct.

  Non-metallic ores will also be subject to crushing, just like, for example, diamonds.

  If you want crush chests from Iron Chests, you can do it!**


Supported Mods:

Ad Astra;

Alex`s Caves;

AoA3; 

Darker Depths; 

Divine RPG; 

Ice And Fire; 

Iron Chests; 

Tinkers Construct; 

Wyrmroost;



